<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome to 9ja Market</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #009933;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        color: white;
        border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-top: none;
        border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
      }
      h1,
      h2 {
        color: #009933;
      }
      .steps {
        margin: 20px 0;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }
      .steps li {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .highlight {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
        padding: 15px;
        border-left: 4px solid #009933;
        margin: 15px 0;
      }
      .footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.9em;
        color: #666;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome to 9ja Market!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Dear <%= brandName %> Team,</h2>

      <p>
        Thank you for joining 9ja Market! We're thrilled to have you as part of
        our growing community of merchants connecting with customers across
        Nigeria.
      </p>

      <div class="highlight">
        <strong
          >Your brand "<%= brandName %>" is now live on our platform!</strong
        >
      </div>

      <h3>Here's how to get started:</h3>

      <ol class="steps">
        <li>
          <strong>Complete your profile</strong> - Add your business
          information, operating hours, and contact details to help customers
          find you.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Upload your products</strong> - Showcase your inventory with
          high-quality images and detailed descriptions. Each product will be
          listed under your brand name within your market category.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Promote with ads</strong> - Give your products prime
          visibility by clicking "Run Ad" on selected items. Advertised products
          appear first in search results and on the main page, both
          platform-wide and within your specific market.
        </li>

        <li>
          <strong>Track your performance</strong> - Monitor your sales, customer
          interactions, and most popular products through your merchant
          dashboard.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <div class="highlight">
        <p>
          <strong>Pro Tip:</strong> Products with multiple clear images and
          detailed descriptions typically sell 3x faster!
        </p>
      </div>

      <p>
        Our platform makes it easy to connect with customers in your local
        market and across Nigeria. You can also process orders, manage
        inventory, and handle secure transactions all in one place.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you have any questions or need assistance, our merchant support team
        is available to help you succeed.
      </p>

      <p>
        Best regards,<br />
        The 9ja Market Team
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        <p>Â© 9ja Market - Connecting Local Markets Across Nigeria</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
